n set up in Doti District Hospital after he tested positive for the coronavirus.\n\nMeanwhile, Bohara managed to break through the security fence and fled around 10:30 pm on Thursday.\n\nSudurpaschim Police informed that further investigation into the incident is underway.","title":"3 policemen suspended after murder accused flees from hospital - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/04/146547/","video":[]}
